{"tid":853953,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"廿六歲上車 vs 廿六歲住老母間公屋","createTime":"2018-10-09T03:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T05:53:52.000Z","uid":43146,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7cdfe49fcf85359096429a65549120462254343e","tid":853953,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:55:33.000Z","msg":"美聯物業梁文楓表示，二手樓市交投慘淡，青衣終靠一宗劈價成交，打破本月零成交冰河僵局，更形容為「第一滴血」。<br />\n他表示，單位為美景花園5座高層G室，實用面積329方呎，業主是一對年過40歲兩夫婦，單位已交吉，今年8月放盤，叫價530萬元，當時屬市價，堅持38天，最終堅持不了，面對現實，大幅減價近一成以480萬元沽出，呎價14,590元。<br />\n代理透露今天買賣雙方交易過程，買家和業主都在該代理分行「擺枱」傾價，業主今天的價錢已調低至500萬元，講明無得再減，買家是一名年約26歲的青年，堅持只肯出價480萬元，雙方對恃兩小時，期間代理費盡唇舌，業主在極不情願終減多20萬元賣樓。代理更指，女方於離開分行時更眼濕濕，很不開心喊住離開。<br />\n賣方是1999年以135萬購入，雖然今次以低價賣樓，但賬面仍賺345萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181008/58772257\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F58772257&d=sZljDrWenY9hBEOu%2BnkSMywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=f37a6905\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F58772257&h=0d17914f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181008/58772257</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廿六歲上車<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廿六歲住老母間公屋"},{"pid":"6686b8b4e11f7e2134fd5c2b2c4fc07c3f2757df","tid":853953,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:56:21.000Z","msg":"26歲上車算叻仔"},{"pid":"04dbeffc0336b9953331961d50a330a7c00a3cd1","tid":853953,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6686b8b4e11f7e2134fd5c2b2c4fc07c3f2757df","tid":853953,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:56:21.000Z","msg":"26歲上車算叻仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:58:59.000Z","msg":